title: Women of iHeartCountry with Amy Brown: Guest Cam
itunes:title: Women of iHeartCountry with Amy Brown: Guest Cam
description:
A special edition of a Women of iHeartCountry interview and performance. Amy welcomes Cam! Amy and Cam talked about her new single, motherhood and getting to open up recently for Eric Church. She also performed her song “Burning House”. And be sure to check out Women of iHeartCountry on your local iHeartCountry station every weekend hosted by Amy!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
